# File Organizer Automation

This project is a simple Python automation script that organizes files in a folder into different subfolders based on file type.

## üîß Features
- Automatically scans all files in a given directory  
- Separates files into folders like:
  - Images (jpg, jpeg, png)
  - Documents (pdf, docx, txt)
  - Videos (mp4, mkv)
  - Others (remaining file types)
- Creates folders automatically if they don‚Äôt exist

